## Stack

| Concern     | Choice                          |
|-------------|---------------------------------|
| Router      | chi v5                          |
[[ if .HasDatabase ]]| Database    | PostgreSQL via pgx/v5[[ if .HasDBTooling ]] + sqlc[[ end ]]    |
[[ end ]][[ if .HasMigrations ]]| Migrations  | goose                           |
