## Quick start

```bash
# Copy and edit environment variables
cp .env.example .env
[[ if .HasDatabase ]]
# Create the database
createdb [[ .ProjectName ]]
[[ end ]][[ if .HasMigrations ]]
# Run migrations
make migrate-up
[[ end ]]
# Build and run
make build
./[[ .ProjectName ]]

# Verify
curl -s http://localhost:8080/healthz | jq .
```

